    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely spotless. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It runs like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car smell. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
