    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and is finished in its original, deep-gloss factory paint, which has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. The interior remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV damage, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of service records, all performed by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, showing no signs of leaks or age. With low mileage and a flawless history, this is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking the absolute best example on the market. Sale includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
