    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! I have babied this car from day one, and it is in truly stunning, like-new condition. It drives like a total dream and looks just as gorgeous as the day it was first bought. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. It\u2019s spotless inside and out\u2014you won't find a single thing out of place! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
