    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2018 BMW M2 Competition, a masterclass in longitudinal dynamics. Powered by the S55 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, this unit delivers a linear power band optimized by high-precision direct injection and Valvetronic variable valve timing. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring the factory-spec CFRP high-precision strut brace for maximum torsional rigidity. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with an Active M Differential, the drivetrain provides exceptional torque vectoring. This example boasts a factory-original finish with zero paint correction required and an interior devoid of bolster wear. Mechanically stock and meticulously maintained, it represents a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
